    <p class="govuk-body">This guide is for anyone who needs to explain the Department for Education’s pilot offer to increase mobile data allowances for children and young people.</p>

    <p class="govuk-body">It helps you tell people what’s available and collect the information you need to submit.</p>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="who-can-get-help">Who can get help</h3>

    <%= render partial: 'shared/pilot_mno_offer_eligibility' %>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="what-information-youll-need-to-collect">What information you’ll need to collect</h3>

    <p class="govuk-body">To request extra mobile data for an eligible person we need you to collect the following information:</p>

    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>the account holder’s name</li>
      <li>their mobile number (a number beginning with ‘07’)</li>
      <li>their mobile network</li>
      <li>whether they pay monthly or pay as they go</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="govuk-body">You also need to explain our privacy policy to the account holder.</p>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m" id="how-to-save-information">How to save information</h3>

    <p class="govuk-body">Use one of the following template spreadsheets to save the information you’re collecting:</p>

    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <!-- <li><%= govuk_link_to 'Google Sheets spreadsheet', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/15bOT-wNAM_GunPNbuXxDD3sz0a-ej75r/view' %></li> -->
      <li><%= govuk_link_to 'Excel Spreadsheet', '/collecting-mobile-information/extra-mobile-data-requests-template.xlsx' %></li>
    </ul>

    <p class="govuk-body">Return the completed spreadsheet to the local authority or trust that approached you about this scheme.</p>

    <%= render partial: 'shared/guide_navigation' %>
